Class GraphADT

java.lang.Object
graph.GraphADT
public class GraphADT
extends java.lang.Object
GraphADT represents a mutable directed labeled graph of nodes Spec fields:
Specfield:
lst : List // List of nodes, size : int // size of graph Abstract Invariant: No nodes in graph may contain exactly the same data
